graph TB
    subgraph "Kubeflow Training Operator"
        Controller[Training Operator Controller]
        Webhook[Webhook Server<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS]
        Metrics[Metrics Server<br/>8080/TCP HTTP]
        Health[Health Server<br/>8081/TCP HTTP]

        subgraph "Framework Controllers"
            PyTorchCtrl[PyTorchJob Controller]
            TFCtrl[TFJob Controller]
            XGBoostCtrl[XGBoostJob Controller]
            MPICtrl[MPIJob Controller]
            PaddleCtrl[PaddleJob Controller]
            JAXCtrl[JAXJob Controller]
        end

        Controller --> PyTorchCtrl
        Controller --> TFCtrl
        Controller --> XGBoostCtrl
        Controller --> MPICtrl
        Controller --> PaddleCtrl
        Controller --> JAXCtrl
    end

    User[Data Scientist] -->|creates| PyTorchJobCR[PyTorchJob CR]
    User -->|creates| TFJobCR[TFJob CR]
    User -->|creates| XGBoostJobCR[XGBoostJob CR]
    User -->|creates| MPIJobCR[MPIJob CR]
    User -->|creates| PaddleJobCR[PaddleJob CR]
    User -->|creates| JAXJobCR[JAXJob CR]

    PyTorchJobCR -->|validates| Webhook
    TFJobCR -->|validates| Webhook
    XGBoostJobCR -->|validates| Webhook
    MPIJobCR -->|validates| Webhook
    PaddleJobCR -->|validates| Webhook
    JAXJobCR -->|validates| Webhook

    PyTorchJobCR -->|watched by| PyTorchCtrl
    TFJobCR -->|watched by| TFCtrl
    XGBoostJobCR -->|watched by| XGBoostCtrl
    MPIJobCR -->|watched by| MPICtrl
    PaddleJobCR -->|watched by| PaddleCtrl
    JAXJobCR -->|watched by| JAXCtrl

    PyTorchCtrl -->|creates| MasterPod[Master Pod]
    PyTorchCtrl -->|creates| WorkerPods[Worker Pods]
    PyTorchCtrl -->|creates| Services[Services<br/>master-0: 23456/TCP]
    PyTorchCtrl -->|creates| NetworkPolicies[NetworkPolicies]

    Controller -->|optionally creates| PodGroup[PodGroup<br/>Gang Scheduling]

    Controller -->|depends on| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server]
    Controller -->|integrates| Volcano[Volcano Scheduler<br/>Optional]
    Controller -->|integrates| SchedulerPlugins[Scheduler Plugins<br/>Optional]
    Metrics -->|scraped by| Prometheus[Prometheus]

